      • hasAppointments

        public boolean hasAppointments()
        This method verifies if customer has any appointments scheduled. A list is created and populated with all appointments in the database. Each Appointment is evaluated if it has a matching customer ID number as this Customer object.
        Returns:
        Returns true if customer ID number is found, false if customer ID is not found in appointments table.

      • getCustomerAppointmentList

        public javafx.collections.ObservableList<Appointment> getCustomerAppointmentList()
        This method compiles a list of all appointments with this customer. Two lists are created. One with all Appointments and one for all appointments associated with this Customer object's customer ID number.
        Returns:
        Returns list of Appointment objects where customer ID matches this customer ID.
